Business Brief -- Baxter International Inc.:
   Unit Signs Pact to Supply
   Plasma Products to Group
Baxter Healthcare is the principal subsidiary of Baxter
International Inc., Deerfield, Ill. American Healthcare of
San Diego, owned by a large health care network, represents
more than 1,000 not-forprofit health care facilities.
   Under the terms of the agreement, which takes effect March
2, Baxter Hyland will supply American Healthcare with
Buminate, Gammagard and Hemofil M. In 1991, the national
market for this category of products exceeded $800 million.